title: Can the writing of the ballot papers for Trump in Georgia elect him to the U.S. Senate?
subtitle: Social newspapers urged conservatives to vote for US President Donald Trump in races where he was not a candidate.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: In the elections to the Senate of Georgia on January 5, 2021, he will be elected by the majority of the ballot papers in Trump in the United States Senate, or instead, the Republican candidates will be undermined.
